        		                            Questions? Please contact us.</h4>

                                        <h4><a href="info@explorersedge.ca">kate@explorersedge.ca</a></h4>
                                        <h4><a href="http://www.explorersedge.ca">www.explorersedge.ca</a></a></h4>
        		                    </div><!--end .col-md-4-->
        		                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-6 contact-email">

        		                        <h4>
        		                            Â© Copyright Show Us Your Canada 2017</h4>
